053    public static <T extends PagedQueryResourceRequest<T, TResult>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelQueryDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T query(
054            final T request, final TQuery queryDsl) {
055        PagedQueryResourceRequest<T, TResult> updatedRequest = queryDsl.limit() != null
056                ? request.withLimit(queryDsl.limit())
057                : request;
058        updatedRequest = queryDsl.offset() != null ? updatedRequest.withOffset(queryDsl.offset()) : updatedRequest;
059        updatedRequest = queryDsl.fetchTotal() != null ? updatedRequest.withWithTotal(queryDsl.fetchTotal())
060                : updatedRequest;
061        for (QuerySort<?> querySort : queryDsl.sort()) {
062            updatedRequest = updatedRequest.addSort(querySort.toSphereSort());
063        }
064        for (QueryPredicate<?> queryPredicate : queryDsl.predicates()) {
065            updatedRequest = updatedRequest.addWhere(queryPredicate.toSphereQuery());
066        }
067        for (ExpansionPath<?> expansionPath : queryDsl.expansionPaths()) {
068            updatedRequest = updatedRequest.addWhere(expansionPath.toSphereExpand());
069        }
070        return updatedRequest.asPagedQueryResourceRequestToBaseType();
071    }
072
073    public static <T extends PagedQueryResourceRequest<T, TResult>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelQueryDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T query(
074            final T request, final Supplier<TQuery> createQueryDsl, final Function<TQuery, TQuery> queryDsl) {
075        MetaModelQueryDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> query = queryDsl.apply(createQueryDsl.get());
076        return query(request, query);
077    }
078
079    public <T extends PagedQueryResourceRequest<T, TResult>, TResult, TQuery extends MetaModelQueryDsl<?, ?, ?, ?>> T with(
080            final Function<ProjectApiRoot, T> request, final Supplier<TQuery> createQueryDsl,
081            final Function<TQuery, TQuery> queryDsl) {
082        MetaModelQueryDsl<?, ?, ?, ?> query = queryDsl.apply(createQueryDsl.get());
083        return query(request.apply(apiRoot), query);
084    }
